org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.phd

Class AbstractPhdVisitor

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.jcvi.jillion.assembly.consed.phd.AbstractPhdVisitor
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    PhdVisitor

    public abstract class AbstractPhdVisitor
extends Object
implements PhdVisitor
    AbstractPhdVisitor is an abstract implementation of PhdVisitor that collects all the information about a single phd record. Subclasses are required to implement the abstract method visitPhd(...) which will be called when all the information has been collected (when visitEnd() is called).
    Author:
    dkatzel
